    "rationale": "All 13 credibility factors assessed or flagged; 7 factors assessed with achieved levels below required levels, 6 factors identified as epistemic gaps. Despite factor shortfalls, the package is accepted at Low assurance level for the Minimal profile under the understanding that further evidence generation is required prior to regulatory submission. The declared ed25519 signing algorithm is recorded; however, the signature value was not finalised before package issuance — structural integrity verification via cryptographic signature is therefore not possible for this artifact.",
